public abstract class DigitalArchitectureOMASAPIResponse extends FFDCResponseBase
DigitalArchitectureOMASAPIResponse provides a common header for Digital Architecture OMAS managed rest to its REST API. It manages information about exceptions. If no exception has been raised exceptionClassName is null.
